数据集的生成¶

In [11]:
num_inputs = 2      # 特征值的维度
num_examples = 1000   # 所有的样本数量
true_w = [2, -3.4]      # 初始化正确的w
true_b = 4.2     # 初始化正确的b
features = torch.from_numpy(np.random.normal(0, 1, (num_examples,num_inputs)))    # 产生特征值正太分布
labels = true_w[0] * features[:, 0] + true_w[1] * features[:, 1] +true_b      # 构造目标值
labels += torch.from_numpy(np.random.normal(0, 0.01,size=labels.size()))      #  添加随机噪声

分批处理数据¶

In [8]:
def data_iter(batch_size, features, labels):
     num_examples = len(features)     # 样本总数
     indices = list(range(num_examples))     # 获取索引
     random.shuffle(indices) # 随机打乱
     for i in range(0, num_examples, batch_size):
         j = torch.LongTensor(indices[i: min(i + batch_size,num_examples)]) # 最后⼀次可能不⾜⼀个batch
         yield features.index_select(0, j), labels.index_select(0, j)     # yield可以构造一个生成器
In [9]:
batch_size = 10     # 定义批量大小为10

参数的初始化¶

In [15]:
# 随机初始化模型的参数
w = torch.tensor(np.random.normal(0, 0.01, (num_inputs, 1)),dtype=torch.double) 
b = torch.zeros(1, dtype=torch.double)
# 并将它们设置成可以求梯度的
w.requires_grad_(requires_grad=True) 
b.requires_grad_(requires_grad=True)
Out[15]:
tensor([0.], dtype=torch.float64, requires_grad=True)

模型：线性回归模型Y = WX + b¶

In [17]:
# 定义线性回归函数
def linreg(X, w, b):
     return torch.mm(X, w) + b

策略：定义均方误差损失函数¶

In [19]:
def squared_loss(y_hat, y): 
     return (y_hat - y.view(y_hat.size())) ** 2 / 2# pytorch⾥的MSELoss并没有除以 2

算法：小批量梯度下降¶

In [20]:
def sgd(params, lr, batch_size): 
     for param in params:
        # 使用data属性
        param.data -= lr * param.grad / batch_size # 
        
        # 或者我们还可以使用detach函数
#         tem = param.detach()
#         tem -= lr * param.grad / batch_size

模型的训练，1000条数据，每个批量是10，一共训练三个周期，所以一共要循环1000/10*3=300次¶

In [26]:
lr = 0.03
num_epochs = 3
net = linreg
loss = squared_loss
for epoch in range(num_epochs): # 训练模型⼀共需要num_epochs个迭代周期
    for X, y in data_iter(batch_size, features, labels):
        l = loss(net(X, w, b), y).sum() # l是有关⼩批量X和y的损失
        l.backward() # ⼩批量的损失对模型参数求梯度
        sgd([w, b], lr, batch_size) # 使⽤⼩批量随机梯度下降迭代模型参数
 
        # 梯度清零，防止梯度累加
        w.grad.data.zero_()
        b.grad.data.zero_()
        train_l = loss(net(features, w, b), labels)
        print('epoch %d, loss %f' % (epoch + 1, train_l.mean().item()))

3，自行查阅资料，说一说range是不是迭代器，并分析range在迭代器可迭代语境下的特点¶

range is an iterable, we can get an iterator from it¶

In [33]:
iter(range(1))
Out[33]:
<range_iterator at 0x265f804f9d0>

range objects themselves are not iterators. We cannot call next on a range object¶

In [34]:
next(range(1))

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
TypeError                                 Traceback (most recent call last)
Input In [34], in <module>
----> 1 next(range(1))

TypeError: 'range' object is not an iterator

And unlike an iterator, we can loop over a range object without consuming it¶

In [35]:
numbers = range(3)
tuple(numbers)
Out[35]:
(0, 1, 2)
In [36]:
tuple(numbers)
Out[36]:
(0, 1, 2)

Range is an inert iterable¶

总结¶

·可以跟迭迭代器一样进行循环
·range不是迭代器
·range有长度
·可以被索引
·range中的元素不会被消耗
·惰性可迭代对象
